des:
This skill is a part of Puzzle Games.

In this game, you'll need to solve math equations as quickly as possible. Choose from 3 difficulty levels: Easy, Medium, or Hard. You'll be challenged with a mix of math problems including addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, square roots, and powers.

You'll have 90 seconds to solve as many problems as you can. The faster and more accurate you are, the higher your score! Try to beat the clock and set a new high score each time you play.

Good luck!
If you launch this skill, it will tell you to open Puzzle Games.
